  "title": "BIM Modeller/Coordinator (M&E)",
  "description": "<h2>BIM Modeller/Coordinator (M&amp;E)</h2>\n<h2>Responsibilities</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure the model complies with the standards and objectives outlined in the BIM BEP/LAE BIM GUID and project criteria.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate and coordinate with internal and external disciplines regarding design and model changes.</li>\n  <li>Develop precise construction drawings and extract data based on the discipline's BIM platform.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate design documentation using a methodology that fully utilises BIM software and tools.</li>\n  <li>Utilise Navisworks to present Virtual Design and Construction (VDC).</li>\n  <li>Attend coordination meetings with project consultants and liaise with project members from other disciplines.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and update the BIM model until the build stage is complete.</li>\n  <li>Follow proper procedures for drafting at various stages of issue and authority submissions for assigned projects.</li>\n  <li>Produce shop drawings and as-built drawings, including BIM models if required.</li>\n  <li>Control documentation for submissions, including technical data, shop drawings, and as-built records.</li>\n  <li>Maintain records of changes and updates to drawings.</li>\n  <li>Develop shop drawings in accordance with the project schedule.</li>\n  <li>Create, draw, amend, and update drawings using BIM according to specifications, coordinating with the project department.</li>\n  <li>Independently create BIM models using Revit with a high level of accuracy.</li>\n  <li>Conduct clash analysis of all services independently and resolve identified clashes.</li>\n  <li>Set up and maintain the BIM project and model.</li>\n  <li>Independently create necessary 3D BIM Revit libraries and families.</li>\n  <li>Generate COBie data using Autodesk Revit.</li>\n  <li>Prepare CAD drawings including detailed plans, elevations, sections, isometric drawings, 3D drawings, single-line, double-line, and schematic drawings.</li>\n  <li>Design the layout of MEP services and their routings, considering maintenance and operational space.</li>\n  <li>Attend coordination meetings as required.</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duties assigned by management as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br></h2>",
